21:23.349 --> 21:24.582
- Well, anything but

21:24.584 --> 21:25.850
Canadian bacon.

21:26.652 --> 21:29.020
- I thought you liked bacon.

21:29.022 --> 21:29.020
- Oh, I love bacon,

